WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:15.329 --> 00:00:19.325
Have you ever been served food you've never had before?

00:00:20.195 --> 00:00:23.704
That's what happened to me today at lunch.

00:00:24.650 --> 00:00:28.763
My mommy made pasta with green sauce.

00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:32.929
I told my mommy I don't want pasta with green sauce.

00:00:33.133 --> 00:00:35.941
I want pasta with red sauce.

00:00:36.150 --> 00:00:38.371
She said to try it.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.396
But I don't wanna try it.  It looks YUCKY!

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:48.613
She said I can't have dessert if I don't try it.

00:00:49.313 --> 00:00:54.087
You're the meanest mommy in the whole wide world!

00:00:54.575 --> 00:01:02.171
I want daddy!  Wah wah... WAAHHH!

00:01:03.330 --> 00:01:08.243
FINE!  I'll try it but I WON'T LIKE IT!

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:12.450
And I'm only going to eat one piece!

00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:16.745
You promise I'll get dessert if I try it?

00:01:17.627 --> 00:01:22.439
Maybe I can find one without any sauce on it.

00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:27.324
I'm only eating this because I want dessert.

00:01:27.715 --> 00:01:30.677
Are you watching this mommy?

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:34.171
Mmm.  It's quite tasty.

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.600
I think I'll have another.

00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:39.966
This is really yummy!

00:01:40.570 --> 00:01:43.790
I never thought green sauce could taste so good!

00:01:44.550 --> 00:01:46.760
I ate it all up.

00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:50.580
That was SO YUMMY!

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:53.960
Could I please have some more mommy?

00:01:54.420 --> 00:01:57.590
Sorry I threw a tantrum.

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:01.750
So when you're served something new, you should try it.

00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:04.450
You might really like it!

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:06.830
The end.

